{%- doc -%}
  Karinex Mega Menu — luxury editorial navigation panel.

  Editorial layout (desktop)
  ──────────────────────────
  ┌─────────┬──────────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────┐
  │  RAIL   │  EDITORIAL CONTENT           │  HERO VISUAL             │
  │ 260px   │  Section eyebrow + title     │  Product mockup          │
  │ icons + │  Item rows with description  │  Gradient depth          │
  │ links   │  Animated arrows on hover    │  Floating glow + CTA     │
  └─────────┴──────────────────────────────┴──────────────────────────┘

  Three editorial sections inside the content column:
    · WINDOWS ECOSYSTEM       (Win 11 · 10 · 8 · 7/XP)
    · OFFICE & PRODUCTIVITY   (Office · Mac · 365)
    · BUSINESS & DEV TOOLS    (Server · VS · SQL · Project · Visio)

  Every top-level Hauptmenü item opens the *same* panel — categories
  never disappear and the layout never reflows.

  @param {string} _root - Theme root URL prefix, e.g. '/' or '/de/'.
  @param {object} [parent_link] - Hovered top-level link (accepted for
    API compatibility; panel content is identical for every item).
  @param {string} [mode] - 'desktop' (default) | 'mobile'.
{%- enddoc -%}

{%- liquid
  assign mode = mode | default: 'desktop'

  if _root == blank
    assign _root = routes.root_url | default: '/'
  endif
  unless _root == '/'
    assign _root_check = _root | slice: -1, 1
    unless _root_check == '/'
      assign _root = _root | append: '/'
    endunless
  endunless
-%}

